text: Mihai Botez (31 May 1922 - 8 December 2011) was a Romanian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1922 births Category:2011 deaths Category:Romanian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Romania Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Oradea
